         <div type="translation">
            <p>Sacred to the Divine Spirits. Aspasius, loyal, lived for twenty-four years, 
                      five months, (and) twenty days. Heron and Dynamis and Abdas made (this) for 
                      (their) well-deserving son. </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The opposite face "has <hi rend="italic">fasces</hi> running horizontally across it, indicating that
               the piece is a reused architrave." (Tuck)</p>
         </div>
